This problem is caused by the constant conjunctions evaluating the empty result set incorrectly:
```
mysql> select * from (select k1, -1 as c from test_query_db.test) t where t.c = 1;
+------+------+
| k1   | c    |
+------+------+
|    3 |   -1 |
|    1 |   -1 |
|    2 |   -1 |
+------+------+
```

Expected:
```
mysql> select * from (select k1, -1 as c from test_query_db.test) t where t.c = 1;
Empty set (0.04 sec)
```
